{"tid":1795081,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(奇幻）（短篇）","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T14:36:35.000Z","uid":97887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a90b547665893ecb0cf5a13ca5e3fef42c2fef3","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"晚間，凱兒拖著男朋友的手，看著滿天星海。<br />\n<br />\n「很美。那些一點點的是什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n「是星塵。」男朋友說完，吻了凱兒的額頭。<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，宇宙某角落...<br />\n<br />\n兩隻宇宙生物在吵架。<br />\n<br />\n「屌你！好撚多塵呀！」<br />\n<br />\n「執緊啦！嘈！唔見你執？」<br />\n<br />\n「妖！揚哂出黎啦！乞嗤！」<br />\n<br />\n突然，點點星塵瀰漫著夜空。<br />\n<br />\n「凱兒，你看！」男朋友擁著凱兒。"},{"pid":"854d9e2be02efad5870a506ed55c4f332e6ee603","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9a5deac5a275ca3eee8c149611a3030b3842eb","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854d9e2be02efad5870a506ed55c4f332e6ee603","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21c822eac4b0cd76230d793c532f62f2eb61ef","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f9a5deac5a275ca3eee8c149611a3030b3842eb","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854d9e2be02efad5870a506ed55c4f332e6ee603","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"仲有冇多啲 好鬼鍾意呢類型既故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a5fe35035030dcc89b7c232193cf780f90c698","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d21c822eac4b0cd76230d793c532f62f2eb61ef","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f9a5deac5a275ca3eee8c149611a3030b3842eb","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854d9e2be02efad5870a506ed55c4f332e6ee603","tid":1795081,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"仲有冇多啲 好鬼鍾意呢類型既故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"有好多，因為我個人古古怪怪咁<br />\n<br />\n不過寫完一章無人理就無左意欲寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0654725399f9af6f86c5744a6f3502ed362da4","tid":1795081,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7569e346d73412be2e21f3897e49ae0f941712e","tid":1795081,"uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:36:35.000Z","msg":"傳說，有一位智者。<br />\n<br />\n每次他只說一個字，但是卻可以為人帶來啟示。所以村民都把他安置在一間大宅。<br />\n<br />\n小明有天去拜訪智者。<br />\n<br />\n小明：我鍾意左個女仔。應唔應該表白？<br />\n<br />\n智者：次...<br />\n<br />\n小明：次...？難道說，表白是其次，最重要是她知道我對她的感情？謝謝你，智者。<br />\n<br />\n小明很開心。<br />\n<br />\n小芳：有兩個人追我，一個就賣紙的，一個就賣金的。我應該嫁比邊個？<br />\n<br />\n智者：紙...<br />\n<br />\n小芳：紙？那我應該揀賣紙個個？因為佢雖然窮但有志氣，有日會成功？謝謝你，智者。<br />\n<br />\n突然，一個老婦人闖入大屋，說要帶走智者。<br />\n<br />\n村民：智者唔可以走<br />\n<br />\n老婦人：智咩者？佢係我個仔，自細食雞唔食雞皮，有嚴重語障。只係識名詞，每次用單字講佢最需要的野。<br />\n<br />\n說完，老婦人就帶「智者」去廁所。"}]}